cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.MM

The paper deals with image analysis and machine learning techniques for detecting gastric ulcers in WCE images. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also proposes a novel approach for curriculum learning, which falls under the category of machine learning and could be classified under cs.LG (Machine Learning). Additionally, the paper uses techniques such as feature extraction and classification, which could be classified under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also discusses the use of large datasets and the need for efficient processing, which could be classified under cs.IR (Information Retrieval) and cs.MM (Multimedia).
